<section class="ftco-section ftco-no-pb ftco-no-pt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 img img-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="background-image: url('/Html/images/about-1.jpg');">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 wrap-about px-md-5 ftco-animate py-5 bg-light">
        <div class="heading-section">
          <span class="subheading">Welcome to Counselor</span>
          <h2 class="mb-4">About the Founder.</h2>

          <p>My journey in mental health has been shaped by both academic training and hands-on experience working with individuals from diverse backgrounds. I completed my <b>Master’s degree in Melbourne, Australia from Monash University</b>, and hold a <b>Bachelor’s degree in Psychology (Honours)</b>.</p>
          <p>During my time in Melbourne, I worked with <b>schools supporting students, parents, and school staff</b>, helping them navigate emotional, social, and academic challenges. I also provided <b>Telehealth counselling support</b> and worked in <b>Disability Support Services</b>, gaining experience supporting individuals with varied needs and backgrounds.</p>

          <a asp-action="About" class="d-flex align-items-center mt-4">             
            <span>Read More ....</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="ftco-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5">
      <div class="col-md-8 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
        <span class="subheading">Our Services</span>
        <h2 class="mb-3">We Can Help You With This Situation</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row tabulation mt-4 ftco-animate">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills nav-fill d-md-flex d-block flex-column">
          <li class="nav-item text-left">
            <a class="nav-link active py-4" data-toggle="tab" href="#services-1">Individual Counseling</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item text-left">
            <a class="nav-link py-4" data-toggle="tab" href="#services-2">Group Sessions</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item text-left">
            <a class="nav-link py-4" data-toggle="tab" href="#services-3">Educational Institutions</a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item text-left">
            <a class="nav-link py-4" data-toggle="tab" href="#services-4">Employee Assistance Program</a>
          </li>

        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <div class="tab-content">
          <div class="tab-pane container p-0 active" id="services-1">
            <div class="img" style="background-image: url('/Html/images/services-1.png');"></div>
            <h3><a href="#">Individual Counseling (1:1 Sessions)</a></h3>
            <p>Mind Us offers one-to-one counselling sessions that provide a safe, confidential, and non judgmental space for individuals to discuss their thoughts, emotions, and personal challenges. These sessions focus on concerns such as anxiety, stress, life transitions, and adjustment difficulties, 
while helping individuals develop coping strategies and build emotional resilience. Sessions are tailored to each person’s unique experiences and needs. The duration of these sessions would be 60 
minutes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-pane container p-0 fade" id="services-2">
            <div class="img" style="background-image: url('/Html/images/services-2.png');"></div>
            <h3><a href="#">Group Sessions / Support Groups</a></h3>
            <p>Mind Us also offers small group counselling and support group sessions (up to 5 participants). These sessions provide a safe and supportive space where individuals can share experiences, learn 
from one another, and feel less alone in their challenges. Group settings can help participants build coping strategies, gain new perspectives, and develop a sense of community and support. <br/>
Group sessions are held on fixed days — Tuesdays and Fridays.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-pane container p-0 fade" id="services-3">
            <div class="img" style="background-image: url('/Html/images/services-3.png');"></div>
            <h3><a href="#">Wellbeing Services for Educational Institutions</a></h3>
            <p>Mind Us offers wellbeing services for schools and educational institutions, including counselling support for students and staff. These services aim to support emotional wellbeing, address 
academic and personal challenges, and promote a healthier school environment. We also conduct wellbeing workshops and webinars for students, parents, and educators. Institutions are welcome to reach out to discuss specific topics or areas of focus based on their </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tab-pane container p-0 fade" id="services-4">
            <div class="img" style="background-image: url('/Html/images/services-4.png');"></div>
            <h3><a href="#">Employee Assistance Program (EAP)</a></h3>
            <p>Mind Us offers Employee Assistance Programs (EAP) to support the mental health and wellbeing of employees within organizations. This includes individual counselling sessions for company staff, providing a confidential space to discuss personal or work-related concerns.</p>
            <p>We also organise workshops and webinars on selected wellbeing topics, such as managing burnout, stress management, and maintaining work–life balance. These sessions are designed to be interactive and engaging, incorporating reflective and introspective activities that encourage practical learning and self-awareness, rather than focusing only on theoretical content.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

